                            <comment id="318928" author="adilger" created="Tue, 23 Nov 2021 00:32:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Close as a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10956&quot; title=&quot;sanity-pfl test_3: Kernel panic - not syncing: Pool has encountered an uncorrectable I/O failure and the failure mode property for this pool is set to panic&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10956&quot;&gt;LU-10956&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="318842" author="shadow" created="Mon, 22 Nov 2021 10:52:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt; this error global. I hit same errors in different tests. see  &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15261&quot; title=&quot;sanity: 160j - storage timeout&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-15261&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-15261&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
